<p>Now that our PHP code is updated, we need to actually add the new column to our table.
Since this project uses Doctrine migrations, open a new tab and run:</p>
<pre><code class="language-bash"><div class="line">php bin/console doctrine:migrations:diff</div></code></pre>
<p>All that did was create a new file that contains the raw SQL needed to add this
new <code>stripe_customer_id</code> column:</p>
